attachments.title: Adidas Chameleon fashion fitness tracker and All Day app set to launch in 2017
attachments.text: Adidas might be getting out of the GPS running watch race, but the sports giant is not giving up on wearables altogether it seems. That's because it's working on Chameleon, a new lifestyle tracking wearable, and All Day, a new health, activity and wellbeing app to match. Wareable has been told by a source that&#8230;
attachments.fallback: Wareable: Adidas Chameleon fashion fitness tracker and All Day app set to launch in 2017

text: Keepin it mild cause I love you all, but if the leak had come from Uncorked (which there is absolutely no reason to think it did) it would be Very Bad (tm), so please keep in mind how important and market affecting the information we are privileged/responsible for knowing about is.
